h into JVM and Native Image test runs.\\n\\nThis should reach the remaining `CompileTimeEval$QuoteScope` call sites via the public macro API during test execution rather than compile-time-only expansion. I did not compile or run tests.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_05db16ac799a99ce0169f882da1e24819cb4e828c6c3fc62c9\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 1721, \"output\": 768, \"cacheRead\": 50176, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 52665, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1777894093559, \"responseId\": \"resp_05db16ac799a99ce0169f882ce3e80819cb0c1155c28a8dbe8\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\n3746:  When `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.github.plokhotnyuk.jsoniter-scala:jsoniter-scala-macros_3:2.33.3` is ran this is the error:\n3792:  [Error] /home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge2/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/4985-e8838eb4/tests/src/com.github.plokhotnyuk.jsoniter-scala/jsoniter-scala-macros_3/2.33.3/src/test/scala/com_github_plokhotnyuk_jsoniter_scala/jsoniter_scala_macros_3/CompileTimeEvalInnerQuoteScopeTest.scala:33:57: missing argument for parameter i of \u001b[33mmethod\u001b[0m \u001b[35mapply\u001b[0m in \u001b[33mclass\u001b[0m \u001b[35mStringOps\u001b[0m: (i: Int): Char\n3793:  one error found\n3799:  FAILURE: Build failed with an exception.\n3806:  Execution failed for task ':compileTestScala'.\n3808:  > Compilation failed\n3821:  FAILURE: Build failed with an exception.\n3824:  Execution failed for task ':tckTest'.\n3825:  > Test for com.github.plokhotnyuk.jsoniter-scala:jsoniter-scala-macros_3:2.33.3 failed with exit code 1.\n3844:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_start\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"When `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.github.plokho